item.title: CVE-2023-47145|2024-09-04T19:17:59.293Z -- ibm -- db2
item.description: IBM Db2 for Windows (includes Db2 Connect Server) 10.5, 11.1, and 11.5 could allow a local user to escalate their privileges to the SYSTEM user using the MSI repair functionality. IBM X-Force ID: 270402.
